### Crear servicio de salud
POST {{base}}/api/health-services
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "internalCode": "CONS-MED-001",
  "cupsCode": "890201",
  "name": "Consulta médica general",
  "description": "Consulta médica de primer nivel",
  "healthServiceCategoryId": 21,
  "costCenterId": 2,
  "measureUnit": "CONSULTA",
  "requiresAuthorization": false,
  "requiresDiagnosis": true
}

###

### Crear medicamento
POST {{base}}/api/health-services
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "internalCode": "MED-ACETAMI-500",
  "cupsCode": null,
  "name": "Acetaminofén 500mg tableta",
  "description": "Analgésico antipirético",
  "healthServiceCategoryId": 23,
  "costCenterId": null,
  "measureUnit": "TABLETA",
  "requiresAuthorization": false,
  "requiresDiagnosis": false
}

###

### Obtener por ID
GET {{base}}/api/health-services/3
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Listar con paginación
POST {{base}}/api/health-services/list
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "page": 0,
  "rows": 10,
  "search": "",
  "order_by": "ss.nombre",
  "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Actualizar
PUT {{base}}/api/health-services/1
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cupsCode": "890201",
  "name": "Consulta médica general actualizada",
  "description": "Descripción actualizada",
  "healthServiceCategoryId": 1,
  "costCenterId": 1,
  "measureUnit": "CONSULTA",
  "requiresAuthorization": false,
  "requiresDiagnosis": true
}

###

### Activar/Inactivar
PATCH {{base}}/api/health-services/1/toggle-active
Authorization: {{token}}
